[node name="DescriptionLabel" parent="BOX/CONTENT/bool/requires_bools" instance=ExtResource( 9 )]
hint_tooltip = "Property: requires_bools

Config paths to boolean configs required for this config to be editable.
If a config is not a bool, it is ignored, and all configs must be true.

Configs follow the format of \"Identifier/Section/Config\",
i.e. \"VelocityPlus/VP_ENCELADUS/enable_achievements\"

Config names cannot have spaces or forward slashes,
use ConfigDriver.__truncate_to_setting_entry to help format."
